SELECT [p].[Codigo], [p].[CategoriaId], [p].[Descripcion], [p].[EsDestacado], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[Marca], [p].[Medidas], [p].[Nombre], [p].[Stock], [p].[SubCategoriaId], [c].[Id], [c].[Nombre], [s].[Id], [s].[CategoriaId], [s].[Nombre]
FROM [Productos] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN [Categoria] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoriaId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [SubCategoria] AS [s] ON [c].[Id] = [s].[CategoriaId]

LEFT JOIN [Categoria] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoriaId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [SubCategoria] AS [s] ON [c].[Id] = [s].[CategoriaId]
WHERE [p].[EsDestacado] = CAST(1 AS bit) AND ([p].[CategoriaId] <> 1006 OR [p].[CategoriaId] IS NULL)
ORDER BY [p].[Codigo], [c].[Id]
